snippet.title: Pacify - Gameplay Trailer #1
snippet.description:
Add to your wishlist now: http://bit.ly/pacify_pc

Pacify is a new scary multiplayer horror game. You can play with your friends in co-op mode or against them in PVP. There is also a single player mode. More info in the steam page.

Steam store page: http://bit.ly/pacify_pc
